        "title": {
          "type": "text",
          "$t": "Dolné Vestenice - kresba slovanského hradiska "
        },
        "content": {
          "type": "html",
          "$t": "<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\nTomáš Humaj nám dal pekný vianočný darček - nakreslil svoju predstavu o vzhľade <a href=\"http://www.hradiska.sk/2018/10/dolne-vestenice-slovanske-hradisko.html\" target=\"_blank\">slovanského hradiska v Dolných Vesteniciach</a>, ktoré bolo objavené len pred pár rokmi a publikované až teraz. Na tomto hradisku bolo nájdené veľké množstvo krásnych nálezov z obdobia Veľkej Moravy. V skale pod hradiskom je skalný previs, v ktorom sa našli pozostatky kováčskej dielne. Hradisko je na doslova stolovej hore, takže&nbsp; mohutné valové opevnenie tu nebolo potrebné budovať a postačila vo väčšine obvodu iba drevená palisáda. Iba v severnej časti, kde bol lepší prístup, je vybudovaný mohutný val. Pri ňom bola zrejme aj vstupná brána.Každému vrelo odporúčam návštevu tohto výnimočného miesta...</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhEosQ8oZ4JZvscwFMOr6R6nfPMhMOzePNNvu7ntBxfPaGecx4T7QJrx60kBuqkKv0MkIPKGfwYa7jV_jtdq_6jZFQ6OdAL6eeC9qBEUMAv3PMCdQFB8BP1g6lJ78vQtax4W6JTAzFkTq6E/s1600/48393263_384064458824108_7609739758457061376_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"696\" data-original-width=\"955\" height=\"233\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhEosQ8oZ4JZvscwFMOr6R6nfPMhMOzePNNvu7ntBxfPaGecx4T7QJrx60kBuqkKv0MkIPKGfwYa7jV_jtdq_6jZFQ6OdAL6eeC9qBEUMAv3PMCdQFB8BP1g6lJ78vQtax4W6JTAzFkTq6E/s320/48393263_384064458824108_7609739758457061376_n.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgRJWmXGKc5VkeoSfXZt5otF5KC2ddUG1oCrzmxG9FnNVcBBp4Lu8OW8AXI9bz6y6shicz-jCPFmYACvXrZel4sH-kJCatqmBYW1gbZ0UbJPNnNQJMeRmQkcZ8CWGJSqIS-TWDvqwtLqYVA/s1600/48416134_601936733595694_2105187471493955584_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"720\" data-original-width=\"960\" height=\"240\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgRJWmXGKc5VkeoSfXZt5otF5KC2ddUG1oCrzmxG9FnNVcBBp4Lu8OW8AXI9bz6y6shicz-jCPFmYACvXrZel4sH-kJCatqmBYW1gbZ0UbJPNnNQJMeRmQkcZ8CWGJSqIS-TWDvqwtLqYVA/s320/48416134_601936733595694_2105187471493955584_n.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhtOVTcfd3UncMRqdUKS8flrI-lsAhPHduzwhcm40VPAcAE36YcikncPEHp7oow9qEEs1-9UDrBW7Sf3q-FGchp_ViVmm6dAZEiRsgt0RHqBzHkwGiotCxksFREZdZ6BamchADw63w12MAa/s1600/48428075_200099080943258_5483988181118353408_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"540\" data-original-width=\"960\" height=\"180\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhtOVTcfd3UncMRqdUKS8flrI-lsAhPHduzwhcm40VPAcAE36YcikncPEHp7oow9qEEs1-9UDrBW7Sf3q-FGchp_ViVmm6dAZEiRsgt0RHqBzHkwGiotCxksFREZdZ6BamchADw63w12MAa/s320/48428075_200099080943258_5483988181118353408_n.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjc1oqDpCCxAHK_KuuPYVMVcRW-SoP0_m0KU_DEYIma0AB8usPMrsvhlS2-99oJxjrQ_ldbRiVTeqcLaY6WIYHKYtZ37FLoKPtg-q-UGoKWc5Y_Xxt9-XzXPl4o4R_bLvq2XhEZD41zfMxT/s1600/48987208_525573631277856_43166912405831680_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"960\" data-original-width=\"540\" height=\"320\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjc1oqDpCCxAHK_KuuPYVMVcRW-SoP0_m0KU_DEYIma0AB8usPMrsvhlS2-99oJxjrQ_ldbRiVTeqcLaY6WIYHKYtZ37FLoKPtg-q-UGoKWc5Y_Xxt9-XzXPl4o4R_bLvq2XhEZD41zfMxT/s320/48987208_525573631277856_43166912405831680_n.jpg\" width=\"180\" /></a></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n"
